query:
SELECT 
  p.id AS payment_id,
  p.contractId AS missing_contract_id,
  p.propertyId,
  p.paymentDate,
  p.amountTotal,
  p.principalAmount,
  p.lateFeeAmount,
  p.receivedBy,
  p.channel,
  p.memo
FROM payments p
LEFT JOIN contracts c ON p.contractId = c.id
WHERE c.id IS NULL
ORDER BY p.propertyId, p.paymentDate;
